                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-900 mb-3">{item.question}</h3>
                <p class="text-warmGray">{item.answer}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Evidence -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-primary-900 mb-8">The Clinical Evidence</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-warmGray">
        <p class="mb-6">
          Ultimately, technique comparison must come down to <strong>outcomes</strong>. Dr.
